{"tid":2518013,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[喝水]《世界上的人都靜止了》（4）","createTime":"2021-05-05T17:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:18:29.000Z","uid":52058,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3eb40c9bb19804fdd8027645f718f56c60e046fd","tid":2518013,"uid":52058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\">故事簡介</span><br />\n<br />\n某天世界靜止了，時間、人類和物件都停了。<br />\n<br />\n作家江郎才，鬆了口氣。<br />\n<br />\n一個在靜止世界寫作的故事。<br />\n<br />\n一個是江郎才寫出來的世界。<br />\n<br />\n兩個故事同時展開，靜止世界與小說世界的雙重連載。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">歡迎試閱</span><br />\n<br />\nPost 1：<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/2294284/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/2294284/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPost 2：<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/2358076/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/2358076/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPost 3：<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/2428775/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/2428775/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB專頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/yuyanmr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyuyanmr&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=145f19db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/yuyanmr</a><br />\n<br />\n終於來到Post 4，故事將會加速發展，感謝大家支持。<br />\n<br />\n記得新post留名、正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*每天更新"},{"pid":"bd98012d74df7fbe18b9b390d66692d6c6b4f173","tid":2518013,"uid":228820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"大家見字喝水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ebf646d8f4cd8042eac8fdcd96c6aaddbf38cf","tid":2518013,"uid":30616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"959e294529ea42769309df3780ebe5f4e8bd1fba","tid":2518013,"uid":65901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T18:57:29.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b441e6a38acae850473fafc76d130d6ff7e1fec","tid":2518013,"uid":47762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:04:59.000Z","msg":"新po優雅留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來先生想人催你加速 好易姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無文學咩人開po呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e22e7abc972602acd67951bb781414f97b53e77","tid":2518013,"uid":312860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T21:16:53.000Z","msg":"如何優雅地留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396336417245feae4e9213c82dd51ae0a20a4dfa","tid":2518013,"uid":57162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:52:16.000Z","msg":"見字優雅地飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709895cfdef65400e1118681b0f9df089ad0cf50","tid":2518013,"uid":36044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d99115b544e4cea20b1ff49347164a369ed169","tid":2518013,"uid":66044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:39:41.000Z","msg":"新po優雅留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278c3df37f3f03dfd3e69d7c7b9a0c5029b636f9","tid":2518013,"uid":204481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:13:21.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6a89798370adf19445a670502f63629b08d4c360","tid":2518013,"uid":223498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />優雅留名"},{"pid":"9f0972203136a8aad62aaf22cdc8a5eba07203e1","tid":2518013,"uid":377614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />優雅地留名"},{"pid":"3747ae6a1a078e26048da1d2637b4f386355f8dc","tid":2518013,"uid":200069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"優雅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acc9f8f137f2b19895a0e45211ffb21a0f6fcab","tid":2518013,"uid":308211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ff792e2d48168a326d4b894188c49adaa4e02b","tid":2518013,"uid":208776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"優雅地留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d379c7bed9937f6d402fcbebf06f140bad12c3e0","tid":2518013,"uid":155928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"優雅地飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c811eb2f59c6bb2d3755f7f3a0c3b2193f135555","tid":2518013,"uid":91519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:59:05.000Z","msg":"優雅留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271be86bd23138f4e3d82cb57e9e8e0dd00a3bad","tid":2518013,"uid":52058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:01:15.000Z","msg":"聽了兩個版本的我們，有太多信息需要處理。<br />\n<br />\n但是我看了一下時鐘，午飯時間是有限的，休息一下可能就打鐘了。<br />\n<br />\n「請繼續說下去。」廖愛河說。<br />\n<br />\n她幾乎把重點都寫了下來。<br />\n<br />\n「繼續說第三個版本吧。」黃遙在等待。<br />\n<br />\n我們都同意。<br />\n<br />\n於是連主任又想了一下，決定先說一些開場白。<br />\n<br />\n「第三個版本，也就是對你們沒有影響的版本。」他說，「都是一些跟你們沒有關係的事。」<br />\n<br />\n「你們要聽的話，可以當做一些無聊的瑣事。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n聽到這種說法，我卻加倍集中注意，總覺得會有某種意義。<br />\n<br />\n廖愛河也把筆尖指向了新一頁。<br />\n<br />\n而他卻需要我們給予耐性，等了一會兒才開始說。<br />\n<br />\n「黎智文有他的理想，他就是一個理想主義者。」連主任說，「總是先設立一個理想，然後逐步實現它。」"},{"pid":"cce5d7cdb6253b68b5abc18eda8588933922cf19","tid":2518013,"uid":52058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"「他重視個人的自我價值，重視個人成長和進步，也樂於看到別人進步。」他說。<br />\n<br />\n「可是他寫的邀請信，卻沒有得到回音。」<br />\n<br />\n「其他班考第一名的人，都不理他。」他說，「連回覆都沒有。」<br />\n<br />\n「似乎他們都不想參與這種莫名其妙的組織。」<br />\n<br />\n「但黎智文沒有放棄，就像劉備三顧草廬，也要請出諸葛亮一樣，他修改信的內容，接二連三地提出邀請。」<br />\n<br />\n「可惜，最終他還是失敗了。」<br />\n<br />\n「他沒能組成理想中的未來聯盟。」<br />\n<br />\n我們五人面面相覷，到底聽了什麼。<br />\n<br />\n「你們發現的邀請信，到底是第幾個版本？」他說，「是初版，還是修改了兩次的版本？大概只有他本人才知道。」<br />\n<br />\n「他消沉了一段時間後，身邊有朋友A問他，『其他人就不行嗎？我不能參加嗎？』」"},{"pid":"0d0c4bf28f68b412acaab882f36b14f13d2c4849","tid":2518013,"uid":52058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"「黎智文很驚訝，對於朋友A發現了這件事。」<br />\n<br />\n「原來朋友A早就拾到他的信，知道了他的想法。只是因為自己成績不算最好，才沒有自薦。」<br />\n<br />\n「他說：『黎智文，你知道嗎？在重視朋友方面，我可是第一的。』」<br />\n<br />\n「他還說：『你要搞什麼組織，我陪你搞吧。只要不是搞基就可以了。』」<br />\n<br />\n「聽完之後，黎智文的想法變了，像是受到啟發一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n「他把『考第一』改為『某方面的第一』，例如對愛情最專一的人、對親人最好的人、最重視朋友的人、最注重健康的人，以及最有事業心的人。」<br />\n<br />\n「修改完之後，他就開始找這些人，找回來一起成立未來聯盟。」"}]}